<body> 
<div class="animation-area">
<div class="about-nav">
    <% if (user) { %> 
        <a href="/dreams"><div id="logo"></div></a>
    <% } else { %>
        <a href="/"><div id="logo"></div></a> %>
    <% } %>
    <ul id="nav">
        <% if (user) { %>
            <li><a href="/dreams">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/dreamers/<%= user._id %>">Profile</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/logout">Log Out</a></li>
        <% } else { %>
            <li><a href="/auth/google">Login with Google</a></li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>
</div>
    <h1 id="about">About</h1>
    <div class="about-form">
        <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H2rG4Dg6xyI" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <br>
        <p>This is an app designed to encourage users to pursue their dream in a community format. It was inspired by Barbara Sher's TED talk titled "Isolation is the dream-killer, not your attitude," that put forth the idea of success teams, or groups of people who work together to make each other's dream come true. In this app, a user gets to see, comment on and encourage other users' goals. There are times when everyone gets tired and in those times, when a specific user needs an extra reminder/push, the community members (other users) step in, posting comments of encouragement or personal stories of their journey designed to give strength to the user. This app is for users who value the setting and accomplishment of dreams, be it their own or a complete stranger's. </p>
        <br>
        <div id="how-to">
            <h3>How to use Dream Weaver:</h3>
            <h4>Step 1</h4>
            <p>Login or sign up using your Google account.</p>
            <br>
            <h4>Step 2</h4>
            <p>Navigate to your profile to draft up and publish your dreams.</p>
            <br>
            <h4>Step 3</h4>
            <p>Navigate to the home page to discover other users dreams and help them become reality!</p>
            <br>
            <h4>Helpful tips:</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>When commenting on another's dream either have it be Inspirational, Helpful Advice, or Letting them know that you can help them acheive their dream by offering something they don't have.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Check your dreams # of Comments in your profile to see if anyone has offered any help or encouragement to your dreams!
                </li>
                <li> 
                    Having trouble coming up with a dream? Go <span><a href="https://barbarasclub.com/how-to-get-what-you-really-want/">here</a></span> for assistance.
                </li>
            </ol> </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="home-button">
        <% if(user) { %> 
            <a href="/dreamers/<%= user.id %>" id='home-link'><button id="home">Profile</button></a> 
        <% } else { %>
            <a href="/home" id='home-link'><button id="home">Back</button></a> 
        <% } %> 
           
    </div>
</body>
